Package: DAPRmd
Title: Proteomics Core Differential Abundance Pipeline
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("J. Reyna", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Differential abundance analysis for label-free quantification
    proteomics and phosphoproteomics data using limma. Supports protein-level
    and phosphopeptide-level workflows with optional GSEA and HTML report
    generation.
